This report provides a high-level summary of the transformational scenario pathways developed by the IIASA Energy Program within the framework of the Global Energy Assessment (GEA). These pathways approach the global transition toward sustainable development in an integrated, holistic manner, taking a broad view of the four main energy challenges faced by society in the 21st century: providing universal access to modern energy for all; avoiding dangerous climate change; reducing the impacts of… Expand
